{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775872654326,"sessionID":"ses_285bf45f1ffeoR0P71EELxR1Ub","part":{"id":"prt_d7a4107f1001nyKyPqnhA3PtMo","messageID":"msg_d7a40f67b001pGAbNL0rHgQF4D","sessionID":"ses_285bf45f1ffeoR0P71EELxR1Ub","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_c071666bb4ed47549b8abd73","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-031 вҖ” RBAC Configuration (SA/Role/Binding)\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-031\n- **Module**: manifests\n- **Language**: YAML (Helm)\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: ST-1 Completed (design.md)\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Overview\n\nThe RBAC (Role-Based Access Control) configuration for AgentCube provides fine-grained permission management using Kubernetes native RBAC primitives. The implementation follows the standard Kubernetes RBAC model with ServiceAccount, Role/ClusterRole, and RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding resources.\n\n### 1.2 RBAC Components\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                         AgentCube RBAC Architecture                          в”Ӯ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\nв”Ӯ                                                                             в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ                     ServiceAccount (SA)                             в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentcube-   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentd       в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ workload-manager       в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ router-sa   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ controller-saв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ -sa                    в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                    в”Ӯ                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                    в–ј                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ                     ClusterRole / Role                              в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentcube-   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentd-      в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ workload-manager       в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ admin        в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ controller   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ -admin                 в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ (ClusterRole)в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ (ClusterRole)в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ (Role)                 в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                    в”Ӯ                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                    в–ј                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ                  ClusterRoleBinding / RoleBinding                   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentcube-   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentd-      в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ workload-manager       в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ router-crb  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ controller-  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ -rb                     в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ              в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ crb          в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                             в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n```\n\n### 1.3 Helm Template Structure\n\n```\nmanifests/agentcube/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ templates/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ serviceaccount.yaml          # ServiceAccount resources\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ role.yaml                    # Namespace-scoped Role\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ rolebinding.yaml             # Namespace-scoped RoleBinding\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ clusterrole.yaml             # Cluster-scoped ClusterRole\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ clusterrolebinding.yaml      # Cluster-scoped ClusterRoleBinding\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ values.yaml                      # RBAC configuration values\nв””в”Җв”Җ Chart.yaml\n```\n\n## 2. Data Structures\n\n### 2.1 Helm Values Schema\n\n```yaml\nrbac:\n  # Global RBAC toggle\n  create: true\n  \n  # ServiceAccount configuration\n  serviceAccount:\n    create: true\n    name: \"\"                    # Generated if empty\n    annotations: {}             # Custom annotations\n    imagePullSecrets: []        # Image pull secrets for SA\n  \n  # Cluster-scoped Role\n  clusterRole:\n    create: true\n    name: \"\"                    # Generated if empty\n    annotations: {}             # Custom annotations\n    labels: {}                 # Custom labels\n    rules: []                  # RBAC rules\n  \n  # ClusterRoleBinding\n  clusterRoleBinding:\n    create: true\n    name: \"\"                    # Generated if empty\n    annotations: {}             # Custom annotations\n  \n  # Namespace-scoped Role (optional)\n  role:\n    create: false\n    name: \"\"\n    namespace: \"\"               # Target namespace\n    annotations: {}\n    rules: []\n  \n  # Namespace-scoped RoleBinding (optional)\n  roleBinding:\n    create: false\n    name: \"\"\n    namespace: \"\"\n    annotations: {}\n```\n\n### 2.2 Default RBAC Rules\n\n#### 2.2.1 AgentRuntime Controller ClusterRole\n\n```yaml\nrules:\n  # Core resources\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods\", \"services\", \"secrets\", \"configmaps\", \"events\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  \n  # AgentCube CRDs\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"agentruntimes\", \"codeinterpreters\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"agentruntimes/status\", \"codeinterpreters/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  \n  # Sandbox resources\n  - apiGroups: [\"sandbox.agentcube.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]\n  \n  # Pod management\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods/log\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods/exec\"]\n    verbs: [\"create\"]\n```\n\n#### 2.2.2 Router ServiceAccount Role\n\n```yaml\nrules:\n  # Read-only access to resources\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"agentruntimes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n  \n  # Session management\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"secrets\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n```\n\n#### 2.2.3 Workload Manager Role\n\n```yaml\nrules:\n  # Full CRUD on sandboxes\n  - apiGroups: [\"sandbox.agentcube.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  \n  # CRD management\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"agentruntimes\", \"codeinterpreters\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n```\n\n### 2.3 Template Data Models\n\n#### 2.3.1 ServiceAccount Template\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: {{ include \"agentcube.serviceAccountName\" . }}\n  labels:\n    {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\n  {{- with .Values.rbac.serviceAccount.annotations }}\n  annotations:\n    {{- toYaml . | nindent 4 }}\n  {{- end }}\n{{- with .Values.rbac.serviceAccount.imagePullSecrets }}\nimagePullSecrets:\n  {{- toYaml . | nindent 2 }}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n#### 2.3.2 ClusterRole Template\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRole\nmetadata:\n  name: {{ .Values.rbac.clusterRole.name | default (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .) }}\n  labels:\n    {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\n  {{- with .Values.rbac.clusterRole.annotations }}\n  annotations:\n    {{- toYaml . | nindent 4 }}\n  {{- end }}\nrules:\n  {{- toYaml .Values.rbac.clusterRole.rules | nindent 2 }}\n```\n\n#### 2.3.3 ClusterRoleBinding Template\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: {{ .Values.rbac.clusterRoleBinding.name | default (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .) }}\n  labels:\n    {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\nroleRef:\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n  kind: ClusterRole\n  name: {{ .Values.rbac.clusterRole.name | default (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .) }}\nsubjects:\n  - kind: ServiceAccount\n    name: {{ include \"agentcube.serviceAccountName\" . }}\n    namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n```\n\n#### 2.3.4 Role Template (Namespace-scoped)\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: Role\nmetadata:\n  name: {{ .Values.rbac.role.name | default (printf \"%s-%s\" (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .) \"role\") }}\n  namespace: {{ .Values.rbac.role.namespace | default .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\nrules:\n  {{- toYaml .Values.rbac.role.rules | nindent 2 }}\n```\n\n## 3. API Contracts\n\n### 3.1 ServiceAccount Resource\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `apiVersion` | string | Yes | `v1` |\n| `kind` | string | Yes | `ServiceAccount` |\n| `metadata.name` | string | Yes | SA name (max 63 chars) |\n| `metadata.labels` | map | No | Standard labels |\n| `metadata.annotations` | map | No | Custom annotations |\n| `imagePullSecrets` | array | No | Secrets for image pull |\n\n### 3.2 Role/ClusterRole Resource\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `apiVersion` | string | Yes | `rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1` |\n| `kind` | string | Yes | `Role` or `ClusterRole` |\n| `metadata.name` | string | Yes | Role name |\n| `metadata.namespace` | string | Yes (Role only) | Namespace |\n| `rules` | array | Yes | Array of PolicyRule |\n\n#### PolicyRule Structure\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `apiGroups` | array | Yes | API groups (e.g., `[\"\"]`, `[\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]`) |\n| `resources` | array | Yes | Resource types (e.g., `[\"pods\"]`, `[\"agentruntimes\"]`) |\n| `verbs` | array | Yes | Verbs (e.g., `[\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]`) |\n| `resourceNames` | array | No | Limit to specific resource names |\n| `nonResourceURLs` | array | No | Non-resource URLs (ClusterRole only) |\n\n### 3.3 RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding Resource\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `apiVersion` | string | Yes | `rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1` |\n| `kind` | string | Yes | `RoleBinding` or `ClusterRoleBinding` |\n| `metadata.name` | string | Yes | Binding name |\n| `metadata.namespace` | string | Yes (RoleBinding only) | Namespace |\n| `roleRef` | object | Yes | Reference to Role/ClusterRole |\n| `subjects` | array | Yes | Array of Subject |\n\n#### RoleRef Structure\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `apiGroup` | string | Yes | `rbac.authorization.k8s.io` |\n| `kind` | string | Yes | `Role` or `ClusterRole` |\n| `name` | string | Yes | Role name |\n\n#### Subject Structure\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `kind` | string | Yes | `User`, `Group`, or `ServiceAccount` |\n| `name` | string | Yes | Name (for SA: `sa-name` or `sa-name:namespace`) |\n| `apiGroup` | string | No | `rbac.authorization.k8s.io` (optional) |\n| `namespace` | string | No | Namespace (required for ServiceAccount) |\n\n### 3.4 Helm Helper Functions\n\n```yaml\n# _helpers.tpl\n\n{{- /*\nGenerate ServiceAccount name\n*/ -}}\n{{- define \"agentcube.serviceAccountName\" -}}\n{{- .Values.rbac.serviceAccount.name | default (printf \"%s-%s\" (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .) \"sa\") }}\n{{- end }}\n\n{{- /*\nGenerate ClusterRole name\n*/ -}}\n{{- define \"agentcube.clusterRoleName\" -}}\n{{- .Values.rbac.clusterRole.name | default (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .) }}\n{{- end }}\n\n{{- /*\nGenerate ClusterRoleBinding name\n*/ -}}\n{{- define \"agentcube.clusterRoleBindingName\" -}}\n{{- .Values.rbac.clusterRoleBinding.name | default (printf \"%s-%s\" (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .) \"crb\") }}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n## 4. Error Handling\n\n### 4.1 Validation Errors\n\n| Error | Scenario | Resolution |\n|-------|----------|------------|\n| Invalid ServiceAccount name | Name exceeds 63 chars | Use shorter name |\n| Duplicate RBAC resources | Same name in namespace | Use unique names |\n| Invalid rule verb | Unknown verb | Use valid K8s verbs |\n| Missing required field | apiGroups/resources/verbs empty | Provide required fields |\n| RoleBinding namespace mismatch | Role and binding different namespaces | Align namespaces |\n\n### 4.2 Helm Validation\n\n```bash\n# Validate Helm templates\nhelm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube --debug\n\n# Dry-run install to validate\nhelm install --dry-run --generate-name ./manifests/agentcube\n\n# Lint Helm chart\nhelm lint ./manifests/agentcube\n```\n\n### 4.3 RBAC Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Check ServiceAccount\nkubectl get sa <sa-name> -n <namespace>\n\n# Check ClusterRole\nkubectl get clusterrole <role-name> -o yaml\n\n# Check RoleBinding\nkubectl get rolebinding <binding-name> -n <namespace> -o yaml\n\n# Verify permissions\nkubectl auth can-i <verb> <resource> --as=system:serviceaccount:<namespace>:<sa-name>\n```\n\n### 4.4 Common Issues\n\n| Issue | Cause | Solution |\n|-------|-------|----------|\n| Permission denied | Missing RBAC rules | Add required verbs to Role/ClusterRole |\n| Resource not found | Wrong namespace | Specify correct namespace in Subject |\n| Role not bound | Missing RoleBinding | Create RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding |\n| Orphaned binding | Role deleted before binding | Delete orphaned binding manually |\n\n## 5. Testing Strategy\n\n### 5.1 Unit Tests\n\n#### 5.1.1 Template Rendering Test\n\n```python\ndef test_rbac_serviceaccount_template():\n    \"\"\"Test ServiceAccount template renders correctly.\"\"\"\n    values = {\n        \"rbac\": {\n            \"create\": True,\n            \"serviceAccount\": {\n                \"name\": \"test-sa\",\n                \"annotations\": {\"test\": \"annotation\"},\n                \"imagePullSecrets\": [{\"name\": \"regcred\"}]\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    # Verify template renders with correct values\n```\n\n#### 5.1.2 Template Conditional Test\n\n```python\ndef test_rbac_disabled():\n    \"\"\"Test templates are skipped when RBAC is disabled.\"\"\"\n    values = {\"rbac\": {\"create\": False}}\n    # Verify no RBAC resources are rendered\n```\n\n#### 5.1.3 Rule Validation Test\n\n```python\ndef test_clusterrole_rules():\n    \"\"\"Test ClusterRole rules are valid.\"\"\"\n    rules = [\n        {\n            \"apiGroups\": [\"\"],\n            \"resources\": [\"pods\"],\n            \"verbs\": [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n        }\n    ]\n    # Verify rule structure is valid\n```\n\n### 5.2 Integration Tests\n\n#### 5.2.1 Helm Install Test\n\n```bash\n# Install chart with RBAC\nhelm install agentcube ./manifests/agentcube --namespace agentcube\n\n# Verify resources\nkubectl get sa,clusterrole,clusterrolebinding -n agentcube\n\n# Verify permissions\nkubectl auth can-i get pods --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube:agentcube-sa\n```\n\n#### 5.2.2 RBAC Verification Test\n\n```bash\n# Test controller permissions\nkubectl auth can-i get agentruntimes --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube:agentd-sa\n# Expected: yes\n\n# Test router permissions  \nkubectl auth can-i create pods --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube:router-sa\n# Expected: no (read-only)\n```\n\n### 5.3 Helm Test Suite\n\n```yaml\n# tests/rbac_test.yaml\nsuite: RBAC tests\ntests:\n  - name: serviceaccount-creation\n    chart: ./manifests/agentcube\n    release: test-rbac\n    namespace: test-rbac\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: metadata.name\n          value: agentcube-sa\n      - present:\n          path: metadata.labels.app.kubernetes.io/name\n  \n  - name: clusterrole-creation\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: rules[0].resources\n          value: [pods, services]\n  \n  - name: clusterrolebinding-subjects\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: subjects[0].kind\n          value: ServiceAccount\n```\n\n### 5.4 Build Verification\n\n```bash\n# Template validation\nhelm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube > /dev/null\n\n# Dry-run install\nhelm install --dry-run test ./manifests/agentcube\n\n# Lint chart\nhelm lint ./manifests/agentcube\n\n# Verify RBAC manifests\nkubeval manifests/agentcube/templates/*.yaml\n```\n\n## 6. Usage Examples\n\n### 6.1 Default Installation\n\n```bash\n# Install with default RBAC\nhelm install agentcube ./manifests/agentcube --namespace agentcube --create-namespace\n\n# Verify RBAC resources\nkubectl get sa,clusterrole,clusterrolebinding -n agentcube\n```\n\n### 6.2 Custom ServiceAccount\n\n```bash\n# Install with custom SA name\nhelm install agentcube ./manifests/agentcube \\\n  --set rbac.serviceAccount.name=my-custom-sa \\\n  --namespace agentcube\n```\n\n### 6.3 Additional RBAC Rules\n\n```bash\n# Install with additional rules\nhelm install agentcube ./manifests/agentcube \\\n  --set rbac.clusterRole.rules[0].apiGroups[0]= \\\n  --set rbac.clusterRole.rules[0].resources[0]=namespaces \\\n  --set rbac.clusterRole.rules[0].verbs[0]=get \\\n  --namespace agentcube\n```\n\n### 6.4 Disable RBAC\n\n```bash\n# Install without RBAC resources\nhelm install agentcube ./manifests/agentcube \\\n  --set rbac.create=false \\\n  --namespace agentcube\n```\n\n## 7. Configuration Reference\n\n### 7.1 Full Values Example\n\n```yaml\nrbac:\n  create: true\n  \n  serviceAccount:\n    create: true\n    name: \"agentcube-controller\"\n    annotations:\n      \"eks.amazonaws.com/role-arn\": \"arn:aws:iam::123456789:role/agentcube-role\"\n    imagePullSecrets:\n      - name: \"regcred\"\n  \n  clusterRole:\n    create: true\n    name: \"agentcube-controller\"\n    annotations:\n      \"description\": \"AgentCube controller ClusterRole\"\n    rules:\n      - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n        resources: [\"pods\", \"services\", \"secrets\", \"configmaps\", \"events\"]\n        verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n      - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n        resources: [\"agentruntimes\", \"codeinterpreters\"]\n        verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n      - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n        resources: [\"agentruntimes/status\", \"codeinterpreters/status\"]\n        verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  \n  clusterRoleBinding:\n    create: true\n    name: \"agentcube-controller-binding\"\n    annotations:\n      \"description\": \"AgentCube controller ClusterRoleBinding\"\n  \n  role:\n    create: false\n  \n  roleBinding:\n    create: false\n```\n\n---\n\n*Stage ST-1 completed*","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/manifests/agentcube/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/manifests/agentcube/templates/serviceaccount.yaml\">\nERROR [1:3] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [1:5] Missing , o